In[7]:
clustering <- function(sce, res=0.8, prefix=''){
        sce <- NormalizeData(sce, verbose=F) %>%
           FindVariableFeatures(verbose=F) %>%
           ScaleData(verbose = F) %>%
           RunPCA(verbose = F)
        return(sce)
}
